   "source": [

   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

    },

   },

   "source": [
    "from mpart import *\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from scipy.optimize import minimize\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "ffcd096e",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.047675Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.047129Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.052878Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.052205Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# geometry\n",
    "num_points = 1000\n",
    "xmin, xmax = 0, 4\n",
    "x = np.linspace(xmin, xmax, num_points)[None,:]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "871731d7",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.056080Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.055653Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.059975Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.059143Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Take measurements of step function, note: data might \n",
    "# not monotone because of the noise, but we assume the \n",
    "# true underlying function is monotone.\n",
    "noisesd = 0.4\n",
    "y_true = 2*(x>2)\n",
    "y_noise = noisesd*np.random.randn(num_points) \n",
    "y_measured = y_true + y_noise"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "e874873d",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.063868Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.063263Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.067832Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.067007Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Create multi-index set:\n",
    "multis = np.array([[0], [1], [2], [3], [4], [5]])\n",
    "mset = MultiIndexSet(multis)\n",
    "fixed_mset = mset.fix(True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "5406cf1f",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.072072Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.071549Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.079097Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.078410Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Set options and make regression function\n",
    "opts = MapOptions()\n",
    "monotone_map = CreateComponent(fixed_mset, opts)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "46060cb3",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.085401Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.084921Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.089760Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.088838Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Least squares objective\n",
    "def objective(coeffs, monotone_map, x, y_measured):\n",
    "    monotone_map.SetCoeffs(coeffs)\n",
    "    map_of_x = monotone_map.Evaluate(x)\n",
    "    return np.sum((map_of_x - y_measured)**2)/x.shape[1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "ea175088",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.093822Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.093263Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.097891Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.097140Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# gradient of objective\n",
    "def grad_objective(coeffs, monotone_map, x, y_measured):\n",
    "    monotone_map.SetCoeffs(coeffs)\n",
    "    map_of_x = monotone_map.Evaluate(x)\n",
    "    return 2*np.sum(monotone_map.CoeffGrad(x, map_of_x - y_measured),1)/x.shape[1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "77f8a2ac",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.101234Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.100769Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.106960Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.106360Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Before optimization\n",
    "map_of_x_before = monotone_map.Evaluate(x)\n",
    "error_before = objective(monotone_map.CoeffMap(), monotone_map, x, y_measured)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "57f0e809",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.115174Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:03.114351Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.265648Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.265034Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Warning: Desired error not necessarily achieved due to precision loss.\n",
      "         Current function value: 0.191952\n",
      "         Iterations: 32\n",
      "         Function evaluations: 101\n",
      "         Gradient evaluations: 93\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Optimize\n",
    "optimizer_options={'gtol': 1e-4, 'disp': True}\n",
    "res = minimize(objective, monotone_map.CoeffMap(), args=(monotone_map, x, y_measured), jac=grad_objective, method='BFGS', options=optimizer_options)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "7635ce85",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.269879Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.269291Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.289683Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2022-08-06T19:33:05.289078Z"
    },
    "lines_to_next_cell": 2
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# After optimization\n",
    "map_of_x_after = monotone_map.Evaluate(x)\n",
    "error_after = objective(monotone_map.CoeffMap(), monotone_map, x, y_measured)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "6c4b21c0",

   "source": [
    "# Plot data (before and after together)\n",
    "plt.figure()\n",
    "plt.title('Starting map error: {:.2E} / Final map error: {:.2E}'.format(error_before, error_after))\n",
    "plt.plot(x.flatten(),y_true.flatten(),'*--',label='true data', alpha=0.8)\n",
    "plt.plot(x.flatten(),y_measured.flatten(),'*--',label='measured data', alpha=0.4)\n",
    "plt.plot(x.flatten(),map_of_x_before.flatten(),'*--',label='initial map output', color=\"green\", alpha=0.8)\n",
    "plt.plot(x.flatten(),map_of_x_after.flatten(),'*--',label='final map output', color=\"red\", alpha=0.8)\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
